<plot>Alex Prospect, is on a vacation from school in his home town of southern California, and falls in love with Julie, a beautiful girl who he believes is his soul mate. He returns to upstate New York, and anxiously awaits when he can see her again, only to be baffled by a surprising phone call from Julie telling him to never return. Following his heart and in search for answers, he returns to California to confront her and find out what went awry. Only to discover that her ex-boyfriend he had no knowledge of, has returned.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?254991</url></doc>
